<main>
    <article>

        <section>
            <h2>About the Song</h2>
            <p>
                "Viva la Vida" explores themes of power, loss, and reflection. The lyrics are written 
                from the perspective of a fallen king looking back on his past glory and current downfall. 
                The song became one of Coldplay's biggest hits and is known for its orchestral sound.
            </p>
        </section>